You need the Holy Ghost to help you choose to be thankful.

26:36.359 --> 26:38.482
You feel lonely during this season.

26:42.626 --> 26:48.893
Ain't that many thankful, positive, grateful people in your family.

26:49.954 --> 26:51.276
You might be the only one.

26:53.978 --> 26:55.760
Anybody ever have to talk to yourself?

26:58.403 --> 26:58.984
Come on now.

27:00.045 --> 27:02.608
Ain't nothing like sanctified self-talk.

27:03.629 --> 27:05.551
Everybody take a step forward, take a step forward.

27:06.452 --> 27:08.114
People behind you take a step forward.

27:12.418 --> 27:14.601
You gotta learn how to talk to yourself.

27:17.725 --> 27:19.447
Can I be real with somebody on this day?

27:20.649 --> 27:24.975
What we say to ourselves is more important than what other people say to us.

27:30.682 --> 27:36.090
What we say to us is more important than what they say to us.

27:38.633 --> 27:42.418
Brother, sister, you better learn how to talk good to yourself

27:45.698 --> 27:47.040
You better tell yourself, I'm blessed.

27:49.123 --> 27:50.045
I am blessed.

27:50.225 --> 27:53.270
I'm more blessed than I realize.

27:54.672 --> 27:56.215
I got the favor of God.

27:57.997 --> 27:59.980
I'm blessed in ways I don't even know.

28:00.021 --> 28:01.723
Look where God has brought me from.

28:02.705 --> 28:04.628
I'm making progress in my life.

28:06.811 --> 28:13.682
Lord, in Jesus' name I pray right now, for every man and woman who has made their way to the altar,

28:14.434 --> 28:24.024
I pray right now for everybody who is in the sanctuary, everybody who is watching virtually and worshiping virtually.

28:24.044 --> 28:33.935
I pray right now that you challenge us to celebrate Thanksgiving every day.

28:36.198 --> 28:40.242
When we wake up, help us to see how blessed we are.

28:41.506 --> 28:44.290
Help us choose to see blessings.

28:45.472 --> 28:47.215
Not burdens, but blessings.

28:47.275 --> 28:52.963
Help us choose to be thankful.

28:52.983 --> 28:59.092
Lord, connect us with thankful friends and thankful family.

29:00.054 --> 29:05.802
Raise up friends and family who are grateful, appreciative and thankful.

29:06.824 --> 29:08.306
Give us discernment.

29:10.018 --> 29:11.881
to discover who's a hater.

29:14.185 --> 29:18.493
Give us discernment to discover who's a frenemy.

29:20.437 --> 29:25.686
And Lord, when we're tempted to complain, convict us, Holy Spirit.

29:27.048 --> 29:34.802
When we're tempted to be ungrateful and unthankful and unappreciative, convict us in Jesus' name.

29:36.514 --> 29:40.961
Help us every day, each day to concentrate on your character.

29:43.385 --> 29:46.230
Or your character is awesome.

29:48.313 --> 29:49.996
Character is redemptive.

29:52.820 --> 29:58.890
Concentrate less on stuff and more on you and who you are.

30:01.835 --> 30:03.698
Blessed are now in Jesus name.

30:05.282 --> 30:06.569
People of God said, amen.

30:06.629 --> 30:08.298
Amen.

30:09.304 --> 30:09.887
Amen.

30:11.093 --> 30:13.426
Tell somebody we're gonna have thanksgiving every day.

